 "Welcome to earth, This is Zardus,commander of the
Alliance."

  Major Panzertron cocked his head at the
transmission.

  "The Alliance?" he asked himself. There was no
information of an alliance in the mission breifing.
Perhaps he should thak this oprutnity to learn more.

  He tapped the comm link," This is Major Panzertron,
commanding officer of this vessel. What Alliance do
you speak of?"
